description: This header file defines the interface for a COSA Library plugin, including function declarations for initialization, support check, and unload operations. It also contains licensing information, author metadata, and include guards.

methods.name: COSA_Init
methods.description: Initializes the COSA plugin with maximum supported version and plugin info.

methods.name: COSA_IsObjSupported
methods.description: Checks whether a specific object name is supported by the plugin.

methods.name: COSA_Unload
methods.description: Unloads or releases resources associated with the plugin.
